      class  DFSNumbering<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>> 
      class  STNumbering<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
      Given any edge {s,t} in a biconnected graph G with n vertices, the vertices can be numbered from 1 to n so that vertex s receives the number 1 and vertex t the number n This is called the st-numbering This implementation is based on an algoritm by Even and Tarjan from their paper titled "Computing an st-numbering"
